    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but that feels like such a small bandaid on a massive wound. even if they're working hard, the math just doesnt add up. the tipping points are already happening. it feels less like \"fighting for a future\" and more like just rearranging deck chairs on the titanic. i feel so exhausted just thinking about it. it feels pointless to even be part of a system that's just going to collapse anyway.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
